Make sure to include the rest-assured library in your project. You can add it to your project using tools like Maven or Gradle.

Maven dependency for rest-assured:

<dependency>
    <groupId>io.rest-assured</groupId>
    <artifactId>rest-assured</artifactId>
    <version>4.4.0</version> <!-- Use the latest version available -->
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>
